'''Christopher Robert Margules''' ([[Order of Australia|AM]]) is the Leader of the Indo-Pacific Field Division of [[Conservation International]]. He is based in [[Queensland, Australia]] and has written extensively on the management of [[biological diversity]] and biological diversity planning.<ref>[http://hcr3.isiknowledge.com/author.cgi?&link1=Browse&link2=Results&id=4856 ISI Web of Knowledge]  {{webarchive|url=https://www.webcitation.org/5vDZo3M6C?url=http://hcr3.isiknowledge.com/author.cgi?&link1=Browse&link2=Results&id=4856 |date=December 24, 2010 }}</ref>

